cs.CV, cs.RO, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.GR

Reasoning: 
- cs.CV (Computer Vision) is the most likely category as the paper deals with image-based localization and regression of scene coordinates using deep learning.
- cs.RO (Robotics) is also likely as camera re-localization is an important task in robotics and the paper proposes a method to improve the accuracy of this task.
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is another likely category as the paper uses deep learning to regress scene coordinates and confidences of correspondences.
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is a possible category as the paper proposes a method to improve the accuracy of camera re-localization using deep learning.
- cs.GR (Graphics) is a less likely category as the paper does not focus on graphics specifically, but rather on improving the accuracy of camera re-localization using deep learning.
